room_title: Escape room "Amnesia" by Escape Room Wisconsin in Appleton
review: Just did the Amnesia room at the Escape Room in Appleton. Great time! Thanks Crystal, you were a great game master!

room_title: Escape room "Amnesia" by Escape Room Wisconsin in Appleton
review: We came for my son‘s 14th birthday party with a couple of friends and had an absolute blast! The Amnesia room was great fun, and the staff was amazing at making sure that everyone was comfortable and that we all had a great time. We failed, but we’re ready to have another go at it another day. Thanks!
